{"tid":1890484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【社區大爆發】南韓單日增100宗確診！累計204宗！","createTime":"2020-02-21T08:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T11:01:26.000Z","uid":161430,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bdaa090f2861a6118455191bcc0f86ccbc1b4f3d","tid":1890484,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情繼續蔓延，南韓當局今早公布增52宗確診個案，下午公布再多48宗確診，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>單日共增100宗個案</ins></strong></span>，全國至今累計204宗。<br />\n<br />\n當局將大邱市和慶北清道郡劃為疫情重點管理區，採取特別防疫措施，今後會將防疫重點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>，由防止病毒從國外流入，轉為嚴防國內社區傳染</strong></span>，盡舉國之力克服疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.chosun.com/sitedata/image/201502/22/2015022201758_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.chosun.com%2Fsitedata%2Fimage%2F201502%2F22%2F2015022201758_0.jpg&h=0077d223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecce772fbefd4684a696606fa83efc9a056d43fd","tid":1890484,"uid":201031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"點解香港仲未大爆發"},{"pid":"3ff64ab836b14e11f8ea7379cf48699bd9d2abb3","tid":1890484,"uid":4811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ecce772fbefd4684a696606fa83efc9a056d43fd","tid":1890484,"uid":201031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"點解香港仲未大爆發"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"唔使㗎啦，食花生睇星馬泰日韓暴咪算囉"},{"pid":"f3af295d841c695e0965206d28db626f5930e6d2","tid":1890484,"uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ecce772fbefd4684a696606fa83efc9a056d43fd","tid":1890484,"uid":201031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"點解香港仲未大爆發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"有呀 西灣明星海鮮酒店個包廂度爆咗"},{"pid":"af68c40472d4683e48783e8a1bbf9af365923413","tid":1890484,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ecce772fbefd4684a696606fa83efc9a056d43fd